<bibRefCitation id="EF80A4D2FF86FFF1FE49A5E973FC1AF2" author="Staudinger" box="[483,663,687,710]" pageId="2" pageNumber="20" refString="Staudinger, O. (1880) Lepidopteren-Fauna Kleinasien's. Horae Societatis Entomologicae Rossicae, 15, 159 - 435. Takhtajan, A. (1986) Floristic Regions of the World. University of the California Press, Berkeley, 522 pp." type="book chapter" year="1880">
Staudinger, 
